{"tid":1948264,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞同個救兵Braithwaite都好撚慘","createTime":"2020-03-29T01:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T09:04:09.000Z","uid":165817,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"953ebc7426f2cb83bb2d3dc4af8a93f967b0649e","tid":1948264,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T01:00:31.000Z","msg":"之前蘇九同丹比利傷咗<br />\n巴塞成個冬天就喺度左撲右撲搵前鋒<br />\n<br />\n最後洗咗成1800萬<br />\n用埋西甲特例 搵咗Braithwaite嚟救火<br />\n<br />\n點知冇耐就停擺<br />\n下次有波踢嗰陣 蘇同丹都傷癒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴塞呢1800萬完全冇作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個救兵仲要本身喺雷加利斯打主力<br />\n而家俾武肺撚咗鑊 復賽都有排坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30aabe30c40bd60cf7fb69387d9bf3e3a207d64d","tid":1948264,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T01:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fb0fa28bc1e2c2a8181ab7140103c9ffd39bda","tid":1948264,"uid":3454,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T01:19:53.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩<br />\n丹比利好快又傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91697d7bb8e28e659375964d9830be6666cb56d3","tid":1948264,"uid":132262,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"93fb0fa28bc1e2c2a8181ab7140103c9ffd39bda","tid":1948264,"uid":3454,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T01:19:53.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩<br />\n丹比利好快又傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T01:37:14.000Z","msg":"呢樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />玻璃已經形容唔到佢<br />\n要用豆腐形容"},{"pid":"1c99f2b443f71c8f7e4047f89932eebd4906bfe6","tid":1948264,"uid":73381,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:55:14.000Z","msg":"踢過巴塞都夠威一世啦"},{"pid":"2c3e23a7032be4c616b40819223fdf6